"title": "8288: joy, of Israel",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8288: joy, of israel",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Joy is characteristic of Israel's corporate worship, especially the great festivals.</p>\n<h2>Joy expressed in and through Israel's life of worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:1-Ps100:4\">PSA 100:1–100:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:10\">NUM 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:6-Deut27:7\">DEU 27:6–27:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:4-Ps98:6\">PSA 98:4–98:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:6-Ps132:9\">PSA 132:6–132:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:2-Ps149:5\">PSA 149:2–149:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:29\">ISA 30:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:19\">ZEC 8:19</a>LEV <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech23:39-Zech23:41\">23:39–23:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:13-Deut16:152\">DEU 16:13–16:152</a>CH <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:21-Deut30:23\">30:21–30:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:26-2Chr30:27\">2CH 30:26–30:27</a></p>\n<h2>Joy expressed by the individual as a result of faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8-Ps16:9\">PSA 16:8–16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:10\">JOB 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:26\">JOB 33:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:11\">PSA 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:1\">PSA 21:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:23\">PSA 71:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:4\">PSA 92:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:34\">PSA 104:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:14\">PSA 119:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:174\">PSA 119:174</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:28\">PRO 10:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:10\">ISA 61:10</a></p>\n<h2>Joy experienced by the nation as the people of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:5\">PSA 20:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:11\">ISA 51:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:12-Jer31:13\">JER 31:12–31:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:11\">DEU 26:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:6\">PSA 53:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:43\">PSA 105:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:7\">PSA 145:7</a></p>\n<h3>Joy predicted in prophetic assurances of restoration and blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:3\">ISA 51:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:8-Isa52:9\">ISA 52:8–52:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:12\">ISA 55:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:4-Isa60:5\">ISA 60:4–60:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:10-Isa66:11\">ISA 66:10–66:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:18-Jer30:19\">JER 30:18–30:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:4\">JER 31:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:7\">JER 31:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:21-Joel2:23\">JOL 2:21–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:14\">ZEP 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a></p>\n<h2>Joy at times of national celebration</h2>\n<h3>The anointing of kings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:39-1Kgs1:40\">1KI 1:39–1:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:21-1Chr29:22\">1CH 29:21–29:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:12-2Chr23:13\">2CH 23:12–23:13</a></p>\n<h3>The consecration of the temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:64-1Kgs8:66\">1KI 8:64–8:66</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:1-2Chr7:10\">2CH 7:1–7:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:17\">1CH 29:17</a></p>\n<h3>Consecration of the temple in the reign of King Hezekiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:36\">2CH 29:36</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Deliverance of the Jews through Queen Esther</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:15-Esth8:17\">EST 8:15–8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:20-Esth9:22\">EST 9:20–9:22</a></p>\n<h3>The rebuilding of the temple and Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:16\">EZR 6:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:10-Ezra3:13\">EZR 3:10–3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:22\">EZR 6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:16-Neh3:17\">NEH 3:16–3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:27\">NEH 12:27</a></p>\n<h2>Other nations encouraged to share Israel's joy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:1\">PSA 47:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:14-Isa24:16\">ISA 24:14–24:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:43\">DEU 32:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:1-Ps66:2\">PSA 66:1–66:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps67:4\">PSA 67:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:10-Isa42:11\">ISA 42:10–42:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:48\">JER 51:48</a></p>",
